imdb.plot outline: In the technology era of 2017 the government is developing a device that will teleport items and even people from one location to another. Though the lead scientist in a freak accident uses the device with his friend and instead of teleportation from one location to another, they teleport to a different reality. Will they find their reality or will they be stopped?
